财政部长和美联储主席刚刚离开白宫\NPaulson and Bernanke just left the White House.

2124
01:59:09,820 --> 01:59:11,600
可能政府要出手了\NThere's going to be a bail-out

2125
01:59:13,620 --> 01:59:14,740
不出手不行啊\NWell, they had to!

2126
01:59:15,960 --> 01:59:16,420
是吧\NRight?

2127
01:59:17,500 --> 01:59:19,500
- 我们用担保兑付房贷 - 这些人早就知道\NWe paid for mortgages with collaterals -They knew!

2128
01:59:19,980 --> 01:59:22,640
ATM机回头会取不出钱来的 他们必须阻止这种情况发生\NCash would have stopped coming out the ATM, they had to back-stop this

2129
01:59:23,500 --> 01:59:28,260
这些银行家知道政府会用纳税人的钱保他们 他们不是愚蠢 他们只是不在乎\NThey knew the tax-payers would bail them out, they weren't stupid, they just didn't care!

2130
01:59:28,460 --> 01:59:30,180
是啊 一帮骗子\NYeah, 'cause they're fucking crooks!

2131
01:59:31,780 --> 01:59:34,040
但是走着瞧吧 肯定会有人进监狱的\NBut, at lest we're gonna see some of them go to jail.

2132
01:59:36,240 --> 01:59:37,220
是吧 \NRight?

2133
01:59:37,620 --> 01:59:39,340
大银行会被拆分\NWe need to gonna have to break up the banks

2134
01:59:41,020 --> 01:59:44,160
- 不可能再为所欲为 - 我不知道 我不知道\NThe party is over! -I don't know, I don't know...

2135
01:59:47,340 --> 01:59:53,360
我总觉得 几年之内 人们还是会和以前经济危机一样\NI have a feeling, that in a few years, people are gonna doing, what they always do when the economy tanks.

2136
01:59:54,400 --> 01:59:57,460
责怪移民和穷人拖累了他们\NThey will be blaming immigrants and poor people.

2137
01:59:57,820 --> 01:59:58,960
但是马克错了 \NBut Mark was wrong!

2138
02:00:00,320 --> 02:00:05,000
接下来的几年 几百个银行和评级高管进了监狱\NIn the years that followed, hundreds of bankers and rating-agency's executives went to jail.

2139
02:00:05,000 --> 02:00:07,180
证券交易委员会被政府彻查\NThe SEC was completely overhauled

2140
02:00:07,500 --> 02:00:10,320
议会也迫于压力不得不拆分大银行\Nand congress had no choice, but to break up the big banks

2141
02:00:10,320 --> 02:00:12,940
进一步规范房贷和金融衍生品市场\Nand regulate the mortgage and derivative industries

2142
02:00:17,740 --> 02:00:19,140
上面开玩笑啦 \NJust kidding!

2143
02:00:19,420 --> 02:00:21,700
银行把人们投资的钱拿走\NBanks took the money the American people gave them

2144
02:00:21,760 --> 02:00:24,040
