2147
02:00:29,000 --> 02:00:30,340
这次 连教师也跟着被指责\Nand this time even teachers!

2148
02:00:32,260 --> 02:00:35,380
这些都说完做完以后 只有一个银行家被关了监狱\NAnd when all was said and done, only one single banker went to jail

2149
