2155
02:00:54,020 --> 02:00:55,740
你能清算出2亿来\NYou'll clear two-hundred mill Mark!

2156
02:00:56,880 --> 02:00:58,620
可是…如果我们出手\NYou know... once we sell..

2157
02:00:59,720 --> 02:01:01,180
最终和他们又有什么不一样\NWe'll be just like the rest of them

2158
02:01:01,940 --> 02:01:02,880
你知道我的意思\NYou know that!

2159
02:01:03,280 --> 02:01:04,780
不一样 我们不是坏人\NNo we're not, we're not the bad guys here!

2160
02:01:05,160 --> 02:01:09,620
我们没有利用美国人 想要有个房子的梦想来诈骗\Nwe didn't defraud the American people and prey on their dreams of owning a home

2161
02:01:09,760 --> 02:01:10,700
像他们那样\NLike they did!

2162
